        "Description": "Salvatore Bravuomo - Your classmate that surpassed you. Eliminate him and assume his identity. It&apos;s your time to shine\r\rMarco Abiatti - A politician who may cause you some problems. The only thing standing between you and success.\r\rBobby Douche - Local shop worker, kill her in an accident so you can represent the store owners.\r\rCarlo Benvenuti - Cause an accident so you can represent the event services.\r\rCarisio Palermo - Poison his drink so you can represent the wine company he was working for.",
